Allison Sumrall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Allison_Sumrall 0 Allison Leigh Sumrall is an American actress working with ADV Films, Funimation, and Sentai Filmworks, known for her roles in the English-language dubs of anime series. She is generally credited simply as Allison Sumrall. She is a veteran of the former Masquerade Theatre and Generations Theatre in Houston, Texas, and received her education in performing arts from the University of Houston. In anime, she is known as the voice of Mui Aiba from Magical Warfare, Kagura from Azumanga Daioh, Lilith Asami from Trinity Seven, and Taiga Fujimura from the Fate/Kaleid liner Prisma Illya series.
